00:19:58.003 --> 00:19:59.628
- Morning, Santu!
- Good morning!

00:20:00.503 --> 00:20:01.503
Morning, Uncle!

00:20:02.378 --> 00:20:03.670
Good morning, Mingma!

00:20:04.253 --> 00:20:05.461
Coffee?

00:20:14.961 --> 00:20:18.045
