Lines of destiny crash on the hills Where a
small ship also carries the news of a storm

01:02:24.711 --> 01:02:32.711
Still you have to keep walking with a smile
Even if you have to keep floating

01:02:46.336 --> 01:02:54.336
When even the lonely Sun gets covered in the
morning The mist tells stories of tragedy

01:02:56.795 --> 01:03:04.795
Take another path but have to keep moving
Miles to go

