Hot lava engulfs the Pompeii days End
of the day comes the account of struggle

01:04:52.545 --> 01:05:00.545
Still got to move taking measured steps
Have to move determined

01:05:14.336 --> 01:05:22.336
Dreams have turned into cold lifeless
stones Pain draws patterns under the feet

01:05:24.795 --> 01:05:32.795
Still have to move
Have to move finding a way

01:05:46.086 --> 01:05:54.086
Have to keep moving on a snowy night Have to
cover the days of struggle and nights of pain

01:07:14.170 --> 01:07:15.170
Anybody in there?

01:07:16.503 --> 01:07:18.211
Is anybody inside?

01:07:35.753 --> 01:07:37.003
Is anybody in there?

01:07:56.045 --> 01:07:59.711
We are breaking the
lock and opening the door.

01:08:06.670 --> 01:08:08.586
Now, open the lock from inside.

01:08:08.670 --> 01:08:10.628
- Go, open the latch.
- Yes.

01:08:32.753 --> 01:08:38.878
- Is everything okay?
- Your Bengali is very good for a Verma.

01:08:39.128 --> 01:08:43.187
I've studied in Kolkata's Loreto College...
stayed in the YWCA hostel.

01:08:43.211 --> 01:08:45.354
Well, even I am also pretty good
in this regard.

01:08:45.378 --> 01:08:49.003
Darjeeling North Point.
I have many Bengali friends.

01:08:49.586 --> 01:08:54.878
That's great! Now if we can get some food...
We have been starving for the last few days...

01:08:55.711 --> 01:08:57.229
We are arranging for the food.

01:08:57.253 --> 01:08:59.378
But first tell us,
who is that man outside?

01:08:59.961 --> 01:09:02.003
- Man?
- Yes.

01:09:47.253 --> 01:09:49.729
We've been here for the last 5 days.

01:09:49.753 --> 01:09:53.878
He was not there when we entered the dome
or when the sherpas left.

01:09:54.336 --> 01:09:59.729
From the rigor mortis it seems
he's been dead for 2 weeeks.

01:09:59.753 --> 01:10:02.045
But body has not decayed
due to the cold.

01:10:02.086 --> 01:10:04.086
So, what do we do now?

01:10:06.628 --> 01:10:12.295
We have to send the body for post mortem
to Kathmandu via Syangboche.

01:10:12.628 --> 01:10:17.420
This man looks very strange.
He is thin but unnaturally so.

01:10:17.586 --> 01:10:20.295
He looks like he died
because he was on a diet.

01:10:20.378 --> 01:10:24.021
Mr. Roychowdhury, I have a suggestion.

01:10:24.045 --> 01:10:29.503
We can all go back
in the helicopter.

01:10:40.878 --> 01:10:45.354
He is attracted to words like danger,
challenge, impossible, risky...

01:10:45.378 --> 01:10:47.670
It can be the pyramid or the Jarwa...

01:10:47.920 --> 01:10:51.562
I think we should send the body back
in the helicopter...

01:10:51.586 --> 01:10:53.420
Let's get it back here at our disposal.

01:10:53.920 --> 01:10:56.628
Till then, let's hear Mr. Roychowdhury's
plan of action.

01:11:02.253 --> 01:11:06.420
Its just that, we have to investigate
what we have come so far for.

01:11:06.503 --> 01:11:09.295
Mr. Roychowdhury, you don't believe
in yetis, do you?

01:11:09.545 --> 01:11:10.604
And you are not scared either?

01:11:10.628 --> 01:11:16.711
No! You want to know why?
Because I deal with human beings.

01:11:17.378 --> 01:11:20.271
And no animal is more
dangerous than humans.

01:11:20.295 --> 01:11:25.312
Have you ever heard of yetis
pulling young yetis out...

01:11:25.336 --> 01:11:30.729
..of the army school and shooting them
at point blank range?

01:11:30.753 --> 01:11:34.979
Anyway, if a revolver
or a 9 mmr carbine is pointed at it...

01:11:35.003 --> 01:11:37.753
Not just a yeti,
even a dragon will flee...

01:11:39.836 --> 01:11:41.128
I have seen the yeti.

01:11:45.670 --> 01:11:48.628
- Behind a rock enroute Kala Pathhar.
- Exactly!

01:11:48.795 --> 01:11:52.271
So, we should go back to the place
where Santu saw the yeti.

01:11:52.295 --> 01:11:54.479
Because no matter what Santu has seen...

01:11:54.503 --> 01:12:01.312
Or whatever stories the Sherpas have been
telling their kids for ages...

01:12:01.336 --> 01:12:07.003
Or whatever Shipton had mentioned in his
diary... Someone needs to find the truth.

01:12:08.378 --> 01:12:11.670
How did Shipton
disappear or die?

01:12:12.003 --> 01:12:15.378
Did a yeti kill him?
Where was his body disposed?

01:12:15.670 --> 01:12:18.711
Do yetis really eat human?
Etcetra, etcetra...

01:12:18.920 --> 01:12:23.795
And we won't be able to find any answers
sitting in front of this dome.

01:12:28.420 --> 01:12:31.878
Anyway, we don't have much to do
till the helicopter comes back.

01:12:32.670 --> 01:12:36.003
Let's check out the spot.
We might just find some clues.

01:12:36.961 --> 01:12:38.878
- Kakababu...
- Hmmm...

01:12:44.295 --> 01:12:46.461
Whoever it is, put your hands in the air!

01:12:55.628 --> 01:12:56.878
Mingma!

01:13:00.420 --> 01:13:03.128
Mingma!!!

01:13:06.628 --> 01:13:12.128
I asked myself.
Who is brave? Who is courageous?

01:13:12.253 --> 01:13:13.937
Who is the real Sherpa?

01:13:13.961 --> 01:13:15.921
The one who has come to scale Everest
on one foot?

01:13:16.795 --> 01:13:18.461
The one who will catch the yeti?

01:13:19.378 --> 01:13:22.503
Or is it me who fled leaving them behind?

01:13:23.045 --> 01:13:28.378
Ma'am, I am a true blue Sherpa.
I won't be able to live with such shame.

01:13:28.461 --> 01:13:30.229
That's why I came back.

01:13:30.253 --> 01:13:35.670
And Uncle, if you don't take me back,
I am ready to kill myself.

01:13:35.795 --> 01:13:37.271
You do whatever you want.

01:13:37.295 --> 01:13:39.628
But first tell us,
why did you lock them in from outside?

01:13:40.586 --> 01:13:43.795
- I'm telling you, I don't know anything.
- Stop lying!

01:13:45.711 --> 01:13:48.586
The government would have punished you
for leaving them behind.

01:13:48.670 --> 01:13:50.878
That's why you planned
to kill them.

01:13:51.045 --> 01:13:58.086
Please believe me, Sir! I know nothing.
Uncle, you too... Please believe me.

01:13:58.586 --> 01:14:00.253
Santu, please tell them.

01:14:01.378 --> 01:14:04.586
Sherpas are not like this.
Sherpas are never disloyal.

01:14:05.586 --> 01:14:08.920
Yes, I deserted them.
I was wrong.

01:14:09.295 --> 01:14:12.711
But what is this about locking the door...
I don't know, I don't know...

01:14:12.753 --> 01:14:14.003
It's okay.

01:14:15.170 --> 01:14:18.330
Are you going to stay here now or are you
going to run away again from the yeti?

01:14:20.295 --> 01:14:23.420
No, Uncle. Never again.
Never ever again.

01:14:24.211 --> 01:14:29.170
You will see. I will give up my life
but I will never abandon you again.

01:14:37.295 --> 01:14:43.586
- What exactly did you see here?
- A figure. A huge body.

01:14:44.295 --> 01:14:50.170
- Almost like a monkey or a bear.
- And it disappeared when we screamed.

01:14:57.711 --> 01:14:59.003
No, no, I am fine.

01:15:03.003 --> 01:15:05.503
I've been on this route many times.

01:15:19.503 --> 01:15:21.795
No, no. It's all rubbish.

01:15:22.628 --> 01:15:25.920
Whoever I ask, "Have you seen a yeti?"
They say no.

01:15:26.295 --> 01:15:32.378
"My friend has seen." Or "My uncle has
seen." But no one has seen it themselves.

01:15:45.753 --> 01:15:49.628
But it's true. That day almost 10 of us
saw the yeti.

01:15:50.336 --> 01:15:54.753
- I am swearing on Pashupatinath. Right, Santu?
- Correct!

01:15:55.045 --> 01:15:59.795
In fact, Kakababu had even seen yeti's
footprints. It was human-like but much bigger.

01:15:59.961 --> 01:16:02.336
And instead of five,
it had only four digits.

01:16:02.378 --> 01:16:04.628
Santu, look there...

01:16:52.670 --> 01:16:54.836
How will the four of us look for him?

01:17:02.670 --> 01:17:05.312
Please try and understand.

01:17:05.336 --> 01:17:08.211
I feel we are very close
to solving this mystery.

01:17:08.253 --> 01:17:12.812
Caine Shipton also disappeared from here.
He had also seen a yeti.

01:17:12.836 --> 01:17:14.312
Exactly the same way we did.

01:17:14.336 --> 01:17:17.545
And I'm pretty sure this is somehow
connected to Kakababu's disappearance.

01:17:22.420 --> 01:17:27.878
I had fallen into a crevasse and instead of
rocks, I had felt an iron slab down there.

01:17:28.461 --> 01:17:29.670
Iron slab?

01:17:41.211 --> 01:17:43.854
Mingma has even marked the spot
with a flag. Right?

01:17:43.878 --> 01:17:45.670
Yes, Santu but...

01:17:46.170 --> 01:17:48.021
We won't find that flag
there anymore.

01:17:48.045 --> 01:17:50.795
I don't care about the flag.
We have to locate the spot.

01:17:50.920 --> 01:17:53.461
It is absolutely necessary
to investigate that spot.

01:17:53.836 --> 01:17:56.687
I'll go there myself
if I have to. Mingma?

01:17:56.711 --> 01:18:00.271
Yes, Santu. Don't worry.
We'll find Uncle no matter what.

01:18:00.295 --> 01:18:02.312
Excuse me, Columbus!

01:18:02.336 --> 01:18:05.979
Have you seen the sky?
A storm is coming.

01:18:06.003 --> 01:18:09.253
I suggest we all get out of here
the moment the helicopter arrives.

01:18:21.586 --> 01:18:23.836
The helicopter's here.
Come on. Let's go.

01:18:25.003 --> 01:18:27.961
- Mingma, let's go.
- Wait... Listen, Santu...

01:18:28.628 --> 01:18:32.104
Don't be stubborn. Come with us.
You and Mingma...

01:18:32.128 --> 01:18:36.545
You are forgetting Officer Verma.
I am a Roychowdhury too.

01:18:40.128 --> 01:18:41.808
I hope you get more medals and promotions.

01:18:47.295 --> 01:18:49.045
There's nothing we can do...

01:18:58.128 --> 01:19:01.878
What a stubborn guy!
He really is Kakababu's nephew!

01:19:20.170 --> 01:19:22.336
- I was just saying that...
- Hello!

01:20:35.045 --> 01:20:38.545
The path was here
somewhere through the peaks.

01:20:39.128 --> 01:20:41.170
Should we go in that direction?

01:20:49.378 --> 01:20:50.878
- Santu! See!
- The flag...

01:20:51.295 --> 01:20:53.615
- There it is! We found it! Let's go.
- Let's go, let's go.

01:27:10.878 --> 01:27:14.128
Santu! Found the iron slab!

01:27:16.670 --> 01:27:17.920
We found the iron slab!

01:28:03.920 --> 01:28:07.003
I have a feeling you are minnow,
not the shark.

01:28:07.336 --> 01:28:12.878
Should I guess your name
or just presume you are Dr. Livingstone?

01:28:15.670 --> 01:28:19.420
Stop fooling around Roychowdhury
and just stay where you are.

01:28:19.670 --> 01:28:21.711
Wow! You are a Bengali recruit!

01:28:22.461 --> 01:28:27.086
There are so many international agents around
but they still sent a Bengali yeti to kill me?

01:28:27.336 --> 01:28:32.086
Yes! Because we wanted your last words
to be in your mother tongue!

01:28:32.628 --> 01:28:34.295
Wow! Fantastic!

01:28:34.336 --> 01:28:40.253
I have a nagging question
which only you can answer.

01:28:41.003 --> 01:28:44.170
Are yetis from West Bengal or East Bengal?

01:28:45.503 --> 01:28:46.795
You'll know the answer soon.

01:28:48.378 --> 01:28:51.586
My revolver has bullets
and I will count till three.

01:28:52.211 --> 01:28:53.711
Time for your last prayer...

01:28:54.461 --> 01:28:55.461
One...

01:28:56.420 --> 01:28:57.420
Two...

01:28:58.586 --> 01:28:59.586
Three...

01:29:05.086 --> 01:29:11.021
Did you really think by wearing
this cheap bear skin yeti costume or...

01:29:11.045 --> 01:29:15.271
making those fake
footprints on the snow...

01:29:15.295 --> 01:29:17.295
you will scare me
and I will be scared?

01:29:17.961 --> 01:29:22.396
Exactly the same way you've been scaring
the locals for the last three years and...

01:29:22.420 --> 01:29:28.437
your organisation has been taking advantage
to intercept our defence information...

01:29:28.461 --> 01:29:31.920
to sell it to various terrorist groups
beyond the borders.

01:29:32.003 --> 01:29:37.729
Well, you've got us. I thought the
fake bullet will give you a heart attack.

01:29:37.753 --> 01:29:40.336
Happens to a lot of people.
But didn't work on you.

01:29:40.545 --> 01:29:46.062
Therefore, plan B which is the second way
to make sure you die of natural causes.

01:29:46.086 --> 01:29:54.086
If I shoot, stab or poison you, the police will
suspect something when they find your body.

01:29:55.586 --> 01:29:57.795
They will increase their
patrolling of these parts.

01:29:58.003 --> 01:29:59.920
And it will hamper our business.

01:30:00.711 --> 01:30:03.003
That's why we have to
ensure natural deaths.

01:30:04.961 --> 01:30:09.711
By starvation... The way you killed the Chinese
man and left his body to scare us. Right?

01:30:10.128 --> 01:30:13.336
He knew too much.
So, we were ordered...

01:30:15.336 --> 01:30:20.670
Anyway, let's see how long
you can survive without food.

01:30:24.170 --> 01:30:25.378
Excuse me, Mister!

01:30:28.086 --> 01:30:31.461
I have bullets in my gun, Roychowdhury.
Let him go.

01:30:37.045 --> 01:30:38.086
You don't believe me?

01:30:42.795 --> 01:30:47.271
Wow! Your gun really
does have bullets!

01:30:47.295 --> 01:30:49.461
Congratulations! Should I get
some sweets too?

01:30:49.586 --> 01:30:50.586
Should we celebrate?

01:30:52.128 --> 01:30:53.711
Stop your gibberish! Come!

01:30:57.170 --> 01:30:59.503
- Aren't you going to tie my hands?
- No need for that.

01:31:00.003 --> 01:31:02.503
It's a Persian knot.
Even Alexander had tried and failed...

01:31:02.753 --> 01:31:05.003
Hmmm... An educated villain...
I'm loving it. Let's go...

01:33:10.003 --> 01:33:13.086
Can't we get out of here
through this window?

01:33:13.628 --> 01:33:17.545
No, Mr. Gupta. Its very rocky.
We will die for sure.

01:37:44.628 --> 01:37:45.628
Right in front of you...

01:38:05.670 --> 01:38:06.878
Santu, run!

01:38:15.670 --> 01:38:16.795
Santu, don't listen to them.

01:38:25.670 --> 01:38:28.420
Santu, don't listen to them.
I forbid you.

01:38:30.211 --> 01:38:31.753
Santu, run away from here...

01:38:34.378 --> 01:38:38.086
If you come here, they will kill us both.
Run for your life!

01:38:39.170 --> 01:38:41.045
Go and inform the police.

01:38:54.003 --> 01:38:56.323
Santu, have you lost your mind?
Listen to what I am saying.

01:38:58.920 --> 01:39:01.146
Your Kakababu is asking you not to come.
You must listen to me.

01:39:01.170 --> 01:39:04.128
Santu, you are making me very angry now!

01:39:05.545 --> 01:39:07.465
Kakababu is asking you to get out of here!
Santu!

01:39:11.253 --> 01:39:14.128
I can hear you, Kakababu, but...

01:39:14.878 --> 01:39:16.295
Please forgive me.

01:39:17.295 --> 01:39:19.503
This once I will not be able to obey you...

01:39:20.003 --> 01:39:21.628
I cannot leave you behind...

01:39:24.878 --> 01:39:26.961
If we die, we will die together!

01:39:29.711 --> 01:39:35.146
Santu, stop arguing with your elders!
I forbid you to come here.

01:39:35.170 --> 01:39:39.336
Please, Santu, I'm begging you. Please, don't
come here. Please, run away from here...

01:39:44.961 --> 01:39:47.586
Santu, can you hear me?

01:39:49.586 --> 01:39:51.586
Please, don't come here, Santu!

01:40:48.128 --> 01:40:49.836
Look there! Right there!

01:41:17.670 --> 01:41:18.670
He is running away!

01:41:18.878 --> 01:41:19.878
He is running away!

01:41:20.586 --> 01:41:21.586
Catch him. Catch him.

01:41:30.086 --> 01:41:32.545
- Where did they go?
- They were right here...

01:41:34.211 --> 01:41:36.062
Two of you come with me.
We'll go that side and check.

01:41:36.086 --> 01:41:38.545
- Shine your torch that side...
- Let's go. Let's go.

01:41:40.836 --> 01:41:43.516
There... There... There...
One of them is getting away... Catch him.

01:43:08.003 --> 01:43:09.003
Catch that boy!

01:44:08.086 --> 01:44:09.253
Mingma, don't give up!

01:48:30.045 --> 01:48:32.086
There were a lot of underground caves here.

01:49:06.336 --> 01:49:08.586
Excuse me, Sir.

01:49:14.753 --> 01:49:15.795
I know where it is.

01:52:48.670 --> 01:52:51.545
Santu, are you okay?

01:52:52.045 --> 01:52:54.711
Yes, and Kakababu?

01:52:54.961 --> 01:52:56.253
He is okay.

01:52:59.295 --> 01:53:01.545
Santu, listen carefully.

01:53:01.711 --> 01:53:05.670
Take seven steps and then sit down.
Understood?

01:53:07.170 --> 01:53:08.503
Is it clear?

01:53:12.003 --> 01:53:14.628
After seven steps, blow them up.

01:53:50.753 --> 01:53:58.753
Not just India or Nepal, you've done a huge
favour for the entire world plagued by terrorism.

01:54:15.753 --> 01:54:19.086
I'm sure you guys must be quite hungry?

01:54:23.170 --> 01:54:24.479
Nothing.

01:54:24.503 --> 01:54:25.480
I'll tell you.

01:54:25.504 --> 01:54:32.253
He is thinking if the thirsty can't go to
the well, can the well come to the thirsty?

01:55:05.670 --> 01:55:08.878
It seems like something
is still bothering you.

01:55:10.378 --> 01:55:11.878
How did you know?

01:55:12.753 --> 01:55:15.170
That's why you are the nephew and I'm not.

01:55:15.711 --> 01:55:16.878
What happened?

01:55:17.503 --> 01:55:22.128
No, actually, it would have been nice
if yetis were real.

01:55:23.878 --> 01:55:26.295
I've been reading about them
since I was a kid...

01:55:26.920 --> 01:55:33.461
Loch ness monster, yeti, roc bird,
dragon, unicorn...

01:55:34.378 --> 01:55:36.836
Almost like believing
that the Santa Claus is real...

01:55:38.920 --> 01:55:43.312
The tales we hear, the stories we read...
Almost like being part of the mysterious family.

01:55:43.336 --> 01:55:47.003
We can't see them
but they are there somewhere.

01:55:47.420 --> 01:55:53.086
Like a distant relative who has had
many adventures, right?

01:55:56.420 --> 01:56:00.920
Tch! My entire childhood just seems
like a lie now.

01:56:05.586 --> 01:56:08.795
Are you telling me
you've suddenly grown up?